# juice_adjust.ts — Math Lockdown

Do NOT modify the mathematical formulas or logic in this file without a formal peer-review/approval step.

Protected:
- trueBeFromOdds: decimal conversion and 1/decimal.
- americanToImplied: +100 and -110 style formulas.
- fairBeFromTwoWayOdds: impOver/(impOver+impUnder).
- structureBreakeven: lookup from PP_PAYOUTS/UD_PAYOUTS by platform and flexType.
- juiceAwareLegEv: trueProb - 0.5.

Allowed without approval: comments, types. No changes to equations or lookup logic.
